===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
In bronze inscriptions, {{liushu|ic|nocap=yes}}: a dog {{zh-l|*犬}} eating {{zh-l|*口|mouth}} meat {{zh-l|*⺼}} – "satisfied".

In the modern form, {{zh-l|*口}} has corrupted into {{zh-l|*甘}} and later {{zh-l|*日}}.

